<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>8-173.54</num>
  <heading>Public records.</heading>
  <text>The Authority shall make the following documents available to the public on its website:</text>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>The financial plan for its capital base;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>Board meeting minutes and records; and</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(3)</num>
      <text>All bylaws, guidelines, and procedures adopted or issued by the Board or the Authority.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
